**ENG**
```How to play on iOS:

Step 1: Download Surge 5 from the App Store
Step 2: Tap the arrow next to or after "Default.conf"
Step 3: Tap "Default"
Step 4: Paste this Text:
[General]

[Rule]
FINAL, DIRECT

[Host]
www.growtopia1.com = 103.250.10.160
www.growtopia1.com = 103.250.10.160

Step 5: Press "Done"
Step 6: Click "Settings" and allow everything.```
**ID**
```Cara bermain di iOS:

Langkah 1: Unduh Surge 5 dari App Store
Langkah 2: Ketuk panah di sebelah atau setelah "Default.conf"
Langkah 3: Ketuk "Default"
Langkah 4: Tempel Teks ini:
[General]

[Rule]
FINAL,DIRECT

[Host]
www.growtopia1.com = 103.250.10.160
www.growtopia1.com = 103.250.10.160

Langkah 5: Tekan "Selesai"
Langkah 6: Klik "Pengaturan" dan izinkan semuanya.```
